text.div:
This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/organization-type
  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/us/davinci-pct/CodeSystem/PCTOrganizationTypeCS

name: PCTOrganizationTypeVS
title: PCT Organization Type Value Set - locally defined for testing purpose; an external FHIR value set will be created through the HL7 Terminology (THO) process to replace this value set
publisher: HL7 International - Financial Management Work Group

contact.name: HL7 International - Financial Management Work Group

description: Codes to specify the type of entity involved in the PCT GFE process
